data.description: Located in the country setting of Zephyrhills, you will find this beautifully maintained 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home sitting on a fully fenced 1 acre lot.  This peaceful, meticulously landscaped yard is surrounded by other large lots and quiet roads and offers 2 gated driveways on the property as well as a carport and 2 sheds that are equipped with electric.     As you enter, be prepared to be invited in by a massive showstopper fireplace, freshly painted walls, and luxury vinyl plank flooring. The kitchen has been opened up to offer a seamless flow into the living room and has been updated with new countertops (2023) and an upscale subway backsplash. The living room and family room offer comfort and style with a beautiful carpet center surrounded by the luxury vinyl plank flooring.      The bright and cheery primary suite, which boasts a walk-in closet, has been renovated with a new shower, new tub, and new vanity.  The secondary full bathroom that accompanies 3 generous bedrooms on the opposite side of the home has also been expanded and renovated beautifully.     Located approximately 30 minutes from I75 and about 20 minutes North of I 4, makes this a comfortable commute to Tampa, Lakeland, Plant City, and Orlando to name a few. Schedule a showing today and embark on a new chapter of your life in this remarkable Zephyrhills residence.
